<search>
  <entry>
    <title>网页基础</title>
    <url>/2023/08/10/%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B5%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="html基本语法"><a href="#html基本语法" class="headerlink" title="html基本语法"></a>html基本语法</h1><h2 id="VScode的使用"><a href="#VScode的使用" class="headerlink" title="VScode的使用"></a>VScode的使用</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">网页开发工具有很多，比如记事本、DW、sublime、webStorm、Hbuiler、vscode等</span><br><span class="line">主流使用的是VScode,使用详细介绍：</span><br><span class="line">1.在桌面上新建一个根目录（文件夹），在vscode中打开</span><br><span class="line">2.安装插件</span><br><span class="line">3.新建文件及文件夹</span><br><span class="line">4.快速生成网页的基本结构！回车</span><br><span class="line">5.自动保存	文件-自动保存</span><br><span class="line">6.打开浏览器Alt+b</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">快捷键：</span><br><span class="line">ctrl+c复制	+v粘贴	+s保存	+z撤销	+y恢复</span><br><span class="line">其他浏览器打开：shift+alt+b</span><br><span class="line">侧边栏的显示隐藏：Ctrl+b</span><br><span class="line">代码格式化：	Shift+Alt+F</span><br><span class="line">放大缩小视图	ctrl +加号/减号</span><br><span class="line">向下复制一行：	Shift+Alt+Down</span><br><span class="line">在当前行下方插入一行：	Ctrl+Enter</span><br><span class="line">多行编辑：	Alt+Shift+鼠标左键</span><br><span class="line">下一个匹配的也被选中：	Ctrl+D</span><br><span class="line">折叠	Ctrl+Shift+[ 展开 Ctrl+Shift+]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<span id="more"></span>

<hr>
<h2 id="photoshop的基本操作"><a href="#photoshop的基本操作" class="headerlink" title="photoshop的基本操作"></a>photoshop的基本操作</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">打开： Ctrl+o、将文件拖入PS</span><br><span class="line">新建：Ctrl+ N</span><br><span class="line">存储：选择存储文件格式、名字、位置。</span><br><span class="line">移动工具：可以移动图层、参考线等</span><br><span class="line">标尺：ctrl+R</span><br><span class="line">参考线：按住标尺拖拽</span><br><span class="line">取色：取色工具、前景色和背景色</span><br><span class="line">矩形选框量尺寸、取消选区 ctrl+D</span><br><span class="line">放大镜：Alt+ 鼠标滚轮</span><br><span class="line">抓手工具：空格</span><br><span class="line">撤销：Ctrl+Z（一步）、Ctrl+alt+z（多步）</span><br><span class="line">自由变换：ctrl+T</span><br><span class="line">切片工具的使用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="网页"><a href="#网页" class="headerlink" title="网页"></a>网页</h2><p>是构成网站的基本元素，它通常由图片、链接、文字、声音、视频等元素组成。index.html</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="HTML"><a href="#HTML" class="headerlink" title="HTML"></a>HTML</h2><ul>
<li><p><strong>超文本标记语言（Hyper Text Matkup Language），用来描述网页的一种语言。</strong></p>
</li>
<li><p>不是一种编辑语言，而是一种标记语言（markup language）</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="网页的形成"><a href="#网页的形成" class="headerlink" title="网页的形成"></a>网页的形成</h2><ul>
<li>前端人员开发代码—–&gt; 浏览器显示代码（解析、渲染）—–&gt; 生成最后的Web页面</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="常用浏览器"><a href="#常用浏览器" class="headerlink" title="常用浏览器"></a>常用浏览器</h2><ul>
<li>作用：是网页显示、运行的平台。</li>
<li><strong>五大浏览器：IE、火狐(Firefox)、谷歌(Google)、苹果(Safari)和欧朋(Opera)。</strong></li>
<li>浏览器内核：负责读取网页内容，整理讯息，计算网页的显示方式并显示页面。</li>
<li>chrome的内核Blink</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="web标准"><a href="#web标准" class="headerlink" title="web标准"></a>web标准</h2><p><strong>是由W3C组织和其他标准化组织制定的一系列标准的集合。</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><strong>结构:html</strong></li>
<li><strong>样式:css</strong></li>
<li><strong>行为:js</strong></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id="html语法"><a href="#html语法" class="headerlink" title="html语法"></a>html语法</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1、HTML 标签是由尖括号包围的关键词，例如<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span>。</span><br><span class="line">2、标签的分类：</span><br><span class="line">    双标签：大部分标签是成对出现的，p h1。</span><br><span class="line">    单表签：极少情况是单个标签，列如br,img,也称为空元素。</span><br><span class="line">3、特点：</span><br><span class="line">    HTML标记不区分大小写，建议使用小写</span><br><span class="line">    所有标签都是放在<span class="tag">&lt;&gt;</span>里</span><br><span class="line">    标签关系分为：包含关系和并列关系</span><br><span class="line">    标签可以互相合理嵌套</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="基本结构"><a href="#基本结构" class="headerlink" title="基本结构"></a>基本结构</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="keyword">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>网页标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1.<span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE&gt;</span>	声明文档类型，位于html标签的前面，告诉浏览器按照html5规范解析页面</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">2.<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span>用来定义当前文档显示的语言。	en 英文，	zh-CN 中文</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">3.<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span> 声明字符编码方式，防止乱码</span><br><span class="line">    规定 HTML 文档应该使用哪种字符编码。</span><br><span class="line">    charset 常用的值有：GB2312、BIG5、GBK 和 UTF-8</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">4.<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;shortcut icon&quot;</span>	<span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;favicon.ico&quot;</span>	<span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;image/x-icon&quot;</span>/&gt;</span>标题图标</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">5.注释：为了更好的解释代码的功能，便于相关开发人员理解和阅读代码，程序是不会执行注释内容的。</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!--注释--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    快捷键ctrl+/</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">6.root: images文件夹	css文件夹	js文件夹	index.html文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="标签的属性："><a href="#标签的属性：" class="headerlink" title="标签的属性："></a>标签的属性：</h2><ol>
<li>属性：用来描述标签的特征</li>
<li>属性值：为属性赋的值</li>
<li>特点：<ul>
<li>标签可以拥有多个属性，必须写在标签名的后面。</li>
<li>属性之间不分先后顺序，标签名与属性、属性与属性之间均以空格分开。</li>
<li>属性采取键值对的格式，即 key&#x3D;“value”的格式，属性&#x3D;“属性值”</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="html基本标签1"><a href="#html基本标签1" class="headerlink" title="html基本标签1"></a>html基本标签1</h1><h2 id="标题字标签"><a href="#标题字标签" class="headerlink" title="标题字标签"></a>标题字标签</h2><p><code>&lt;h1&gt;-&lt;h6&gt;</code> 块元素</p>
<ul>
<li>作为标题使用，并且依据重要性递减</li>
<li>属性：align:left&#x2F;right&#x2F;center</li>
<li>特点<ul>
<li>文字加粗</li>
<li>字号随着数字变大依次变小</li>
<li>独占一行</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="段落标签"><a href="#段落标签" class="headerlink" title="段落标签"></a>段落标签</h2><p><code>&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code>块元素</p>
<ul>
<li>可以把HTML文档分割为若干段落。</li>
<li>属性： align:left&#x2F;right&#x2F;center&#x2F;justify</li>
<li>特点：<ul>
<li>文本在一个段落中会根据浏览器窗口的大小自动换行</li>
<li>段落和段落之间有空行</li>
<li>独占一行</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="换行标签"><a href="#换行标签" class="headerlink" title="换行标签"></a>换行标签</h2><p><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></p>
<ul>
<li>强制换行</li>
<li>特点：<ul>
<li>单表签、空标签</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="水平线标签"><a href="#水平线标签" class="headerlink" title="水平线标签"></a>水平线标签</h2><p><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></p>
<ul>
<li><p>属性：size（粗细）</p>
<p>​			width（宽度）	像素 百分比</p>
<p>​			color（颜色）</p>
<p>​			align（对齐方式）：left	center（居中，默认值）right</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="文本格式化标签——行内元素"><a href="#文本格式化标签——行内元素" class="headerlink" title="文本格式化标签——行内元素"></a>文本格式化标签——行内元素</h2><ul>
<li><p>突出重要性，比普通文字更重要。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">加粗	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">strong</span>&gt;</span>	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">倾斜	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">em</span>&gt;</span>			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">删除线	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">del</span>&gt;</span>			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">s</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">下划线	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ins</span>&gt;</span>			<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">上标<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">下标<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">sub</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="div和span标签"><a href="#div和span标签" class="headerlink" title="div和span标签"></a>div和span标签</h2><ul>
<li><code>&lt;div&gt; </code>和 <code>&lt;span&gt; </code>是没有语义的，它们就是一个盒子，用来装内容的。	</li>
<li>特点：<ul>
<li><code>&lt;div&gt;</code>标签用来布局，但是现在一行只能放一个-块元素</li>
<li><code>&lt;span&gt;</code>标签用来布局，一行上可以多个-行内元素</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="特殊字符"><a href="#特殊字符" class="headerlink" title="特殊字符"></a>特殊字符</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>特殊字符</th>
<th>描述</th>
<th>代码</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td></td>
<td>空格</td>
<td><code>&amp;nbsp</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt;</td>
<td>小于号</td>
<td><code>&amp;lt;</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&gt;</td>
<td>大于号</td>
<td><code>&amp;gt;</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>&copy;</td>
<td>版权</td>
<td><code>&amp;copy;</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<hr>
<h2 id="图像标签行内元素-特殊"><a href="#图像标签行内元素-特殊" class="headerlink" title="图像标签&lt;img&gt;行内元素(特殊)"></a>图像标签<code>&lt;img&gt;</code>行内元素(特殊)</h2><ul>
<li><p>定义HTML页面中的图像</p>
</li>
<li><p>属性</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>属性</th>
<th>属性值</th>
<th>说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>src</td>
<td>图片路径</td>
<td>必须属性</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>alt</td>
<td>文本</td>
<td>替换文本，图像不能显示时的文本</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>title</td>
<td>文本</td>
<td>提示文本，鼠标悬停时显示的文字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>width</td>
<td>像素</td>
<td>设置图像的宽度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>height</td>
<td>像素</td>
<td>设置图像的高度</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>border</td>
<td>像素</td>
<td>设置图像的边框粗细</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="路径"><a href="#路径" class="headerlink" title="路径"></a>路径</h2><ul>
<li><p>路径：文件或者文件夹存放的位置</p>
</li>
<li><p>路径分为：相对路径和绝对路径</p>
</li>
<li><p>绝对路径：完整的描述文件位置的路径就是绝对路径</p>
<ul>
<li>从磁盘开始写，如：C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\web1\1.png</li>
<li>完整的网络地址，例如“<a href="http://www.baidu.com/">http://www.baidu.com</a>“</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>相对路径：以引用文件所在位置为参考基础，而建立出的目录路径。</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>相对路径</th>
<th>符号</th>
<th>说明</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>同一级路径</td>
<td></td>
<td>图像文件位于HTML文件同一级 如<code>&lt;img src=&quot;pic.png&gt;&quot;</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>下一级路径</td>
<td>&#x2F;</td>
<td>图像文件位于HTML文件下一级 如<code>&lt;img src=&quot;images/pic.png&gt;&quot;</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>上一级路径</td>
<td>..&#x2F;</td>
<td>图像文件位于HTML文件上一级 如<code>&lt;img src&quot;../pic.png&quot;&gt;</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="html基本标签2"><a href="#html基本标签2" class="headerlink" title="html基本标签2"></a>html基本标签2</h1><h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><ul>
<li><p>无序列表-列表项没有先后的顺序的列表</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：</span><br><span class="line">项目符号类型：type: disc实心圆	circle空心圆	square实心方块</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1、li不能单独存在，必须包裹在ul里面。</span><br><span class="line">2、ul的子元素只能是li</span><br><span class="line">3、<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>与<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span> 之间相当于一个容器，可以容纳所有元素。</span><br><span class="line">4、ul、li快元素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>有序列表-列表项有先后顺序的列表</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">属性：</span><br><span class="line">项目符号类型：type:1 A a I i</span><br><span class="line">从第几项开始: start:数字</span><br><span class="line">指定列表倒序显示：reversed=&quot;reversed&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">1、li不能单独存在，必须包裹在ol里面。</span><br><span class="line">2、ol的子元素只能是li</span><br><span class="line">3、<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>与<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>之间相当于一个容器，可以容纳所有元素。</span><br><span class="line">4、ol、li块元素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>自定义列表-项目和注释的组合</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span>定义项<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>描述项<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>描述项<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">1、dl自定义列表，dt定义项，dd描述项</span><br><span class="line">2、<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span> 里面只能包含 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span> 和 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">3、<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span> 和 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>个数没有限制，经常是一个<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span> 对应多个<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>。</span><br><span class="line">4、dl、dt、dd块元素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="超链接标签"><a href="#超链接标签" class="headerlink" title="超链接标签"></a>超链接标签</h2><ul>
<li><p><code>&lt;a&gt;</code>标签用于定义超链接，作用是从一个页面链接到另一个页面。行内元素</p>
</li>
<li><p>语法格式：<code>&lt;a href=&quot;跳转目标&quot; target=&quot;目标窗口的弹出方式&quot;&gt;</code> 文本或图像 <code>&lt;/a&gt;</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>属性</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>属性</th>
<th>作用</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>href</td>
<td>用于指定连接目标的url地址</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>target</td>
<td>指定页面的打开方式，<code>_self</code> 在原窗口打开(默认值)，<code>_blank</code> 在新窗口中打开</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>titile</td>
<td>提示属性</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</li>
<li><p>超链接的分类</p>
<ul>
<li><p>内部链接:网站内部页面之间的相互链接.直接链接内部页面名称即可，例如<code>&lt; a href=&quot;index.html&quot;&gt; 首页&lt;/a&gt;</code>。</p>
</li>
<li><p>外部链接：例如<code>&lt; a href=&quot;http:// www.baidu.com &quot;&gt; 百度&lt;/a&gt;</code>。</p>
</li>
<li><p>空连接：如果当时没有确定链接目标时，<code>&lt; a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt; 首页 &lt;/a&gt;</code>。</p>
</li>
<li><p>下载链接：如果href里面地址是一个文件或者压缩包，会下载这个文件。</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;.exe&quot;</span>&gt;</span>软件下载<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span>		可执行文件 EXE	压缩文件	.zip	.rar</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p>锚点链接：</p>
<ul>
<li><p>锚点命名<code>id=&quot;p1&quot;</code></p>
<p>链接到锚点<code>&lt;a href=&quot;#p1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h1><p>表格主要用于显示、展示数据。</p>
<hr>
<h2 id="表格的基本结构"><a href="#表格的基本结构" class="headerlink" title="表格的基本结构"></a>表格的基本结构</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span>表格</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span>行</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>单元格</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span>表格标题</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>表头单元格	第一行	第一列	文本加粗、居中的显示效果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="表格结构化"><a href="#表格结构化" class="headerlink" title="表格结构化"></a>表格结构化</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span>表格头部</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span>表格主体</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tfoot</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tfoot</span>&gt;</span>表格页脚</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="表格的属性"><a href="#表格的属性" class="headerlink" title="表格的属性"></a>表格的属性</h2><ul>
<li>width 宽：300	50%</li>
<li>height 高： 400</li>
<li>border 边框的粗细：3</li>
<li>align对齐方式：left  center right</li>
<li>bgcolor背景颜色</li>
<li>background背景图片</li>
<li>cellspacing单元格间距，默认值2，单元格与单元格之间的距离</li>
<li>cellpadding单元格边距，默认值1，内容与单元格边框之间的距离</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="行的属性"><a href="#行的属性" class="headerlink" title="行的属性"></a>行的属性</h2><ul>
<li>height 高：50</li>
<li>bgcolor:背景颜色</li>
<li>align水平对齐方式：left center(中)  right</li>
<li>valign垂直对齐：top middle(中) bottom</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="单元格的属性"><a href="#单元格的属性" class="headerlink" title="单元格的属性"></a>单元格的属性</h2><ul>
<li>width宽</li>
<li>height高</li>
<li>bgcolor背景颜色</li>
<li>background背景图片</li>
<li>align 水平对齐</li>
<li>valign垂直对齐</li>
<li>colspan跨列合并 水平合并</li>
<li>rowspan跨行合并 垂直合并</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id="表单1"><a href="#表单1" class="headerlink" title="表单1"></a>表单1</h1><ul>
<li>标记：<code>&lt;form&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code> 表单	表单域</li>
<li>作用：收集用户信息，由客户端向服务器端传递数据。</li>
<li>form的属性<ol>
<li>action:数据传送的地址</li>
<li>method:数据传送的方法<ol>
<li>post: 安全级别高，速度慢，传递信息量大</li>
<li>get(默认)：安全级别低，速度快，传递信息量小</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>name:表单名称</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="输入标记"><a href="#输入标记" class="headerlink" title="输入标记&lt;input&gt;"></a>输入标记<code>&lt;input&gt;</code></h2><h3 id="文本框"><a href="#文本框" class="headerlink" title="文本框"></a>文本框</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：</span><br><span class="line">name:表单控件名称</span><br><span class="line">value:默认值</span><br><span class="line">placeholder:占位符，提示信息</span><br><span class="line">size:输入字段的宽度、字符数</span><br><span class="line">maxlength:输入字段的最大长度</span><br><span class="line">disabled禁用</span><br><span class="line">readonly只读</span><br><span class="line">required必须输入字段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="密码框"><a href="#密码框" class="headerlink" title="密码框"></a>密码框</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：</span><br><span class="line">name:表单控件名称</span><br><span class="line">value:默认值</span><br><span class="line">placeholder:占位符,提示信息</span><br><span class="line">size:输入字段的宽度，字符数</span><br><span class="line">maxlength:输入字段的最大长度</span><br><span class="line">disabled禁用</span><br><span class="line">readonly只读</span><br><span class="line">required必须输入字段</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="单选框"><a href="#单选框" class="headerlink" title="单选框"></a>单选框</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;radio&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：name必须设为一样的值</span><br><span class="line">	 value关联的值</span><br><span class="line">	 checked默认被选中</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span>定义标注</span><br><span class="line">作用：绑定表单元素，当用户选择该标签时，浏览器就会自动将焦点转到和标签相关的表单控件上，提升用户体验。</span><br><span class="line">使用方法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span> 标签的 for 属性应当与相关元素的id属性相同</span><br><span class="line">    	<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span>标签包含文字以及表单元素</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="复选框"><a href="#复选框" class="headerlink" title="复选框"></a>复选框</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;checkbox&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：name控件名称</span><br><span class="line">	 value关联的值</span><br><span class="line">	 checked默认被选中</span><br><span class="line">也可以添加lable标签，绑定表单元素，提高用户体验</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h3 id="图像域"><a href="#图像域" class="headerlink" title="图像域"></a>图像域</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;image&quot;</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;btn.png&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">创建一个图像控件，该控件单机后将导致表单立即被提交</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h1 id="表单2"><a href="#表单2" class="headerlink" title="表单2"></a>表单2</h1><h2 id="输入标记-1"><a href="#输入标记-1" class="headerlink" title="输入标记&lt;input&gt;"></a>输入标记<code>&lt;input&gt;</code></h2><ul>
<li><p><strong>图像域</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建一个图像控件，该控件单机后将导致表单立即被提交</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;image&quot;</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;btn.png&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
<li><p><strong>文件域</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">文件域主要是让网页浏览者上传文件</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;file&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
<li><p><strong>普通按钮</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">创建一个普通按钮</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;button&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;按钮上的文字&quot;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
<li><p><strong>提交按钮</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">将输入的信息提交到服务器</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;submit&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;按钮上的文字&quot;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
<li><p><strong>重置按钮</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">重置表单中输入的信息</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;reset&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;按钮上的文字&quot;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
<li><p><strong>隐藏域</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">定义隐藏字段</span><br><span class="line">语法：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;hidden&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="下拉菜单"><a href="#下拉菜单" class="headerlink" title="下拉菜单"></a>下拉菜单</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">selected=&quot;seledted&quot;默认被选中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="文本域"><a href="#文本域" class="headerlink" title="文本域"></a>文本域</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">textarea</span> <span class="attr">rows</span>=<span class="string">&quot;行数&quot;</span> <span class="attr">cols</span>=<span class="string">&quot;列数&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">maxlength可输入最大字符数</span><br><span class="line">placeholder提示</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<hr>
<h2 id="按钮标签"><a href="#按钮标签" class="headerlink" title="按钮标签"></a>按钮标签</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    文字或图片</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">属性：</span><br><span class="line">	type=&quot;submit&quot;提交按钮</span><br><span class="line">	type=&quot;button&quot;普通按钮</span><br><span class="line">	type=&quot;reset&quot;重置按钮</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>





